computerization of book catalogues at the columbia, harvard andyale medical libraries ..AF. G. KILGOUR
a project for the computerization of book catalogues at theharvard, yale and columbia medical libraries has three main objects :to increase speed and completeness of information retrieval bycombining the card catalogues of the libraries and allowingpublication of the combined catalogue in book form ; to permitfuture expansion of the information services ; to reduce theadministrative expenses of the libraries .